pirit-delta-frontier-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsidering%20the%20carrier%20is%20consistently%20praised%20for%20its%20comfort%20and%20reliability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20had%20high%20hopes%20going%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20seats%20themselves%20were%20nothing%20special%20and%20had%20one%20slight%20annoyance%2C%20I%20found%20the%2010-hour%20journeys%20between%20New%20York-JFK%20and%20Honolulu%20were%20easy%20thanks%20to%20Hawaiian's%20good%20food%20and%20relaxed%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20arrived%20at%20New%20York-JFK's%20Terminal%204%20at%208%3A00%20a.m.%20for%20our%2010%3A00%20a.m.%20scheduled%20departure.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222596%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20holding%20their%20boarding%20passes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65650d7bfe5bc6545ebcace3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221947%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20boarding%20passes.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20normally%20wouldn't%20show%20up%20to%20the%20airport%20so%20early%20for%20a%20domestic%20flight%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20extra%20time%20to%20check%20our%20luggage%20and%20grab%20breakfast%20from%20one%20of%20the%20airport%20lounges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWith%20several%20bags%20in%20tow%2C%20we%20headed%20to%20Hawaiian's%20check-in%20counter%20and%20were%20happy%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20few%20people%20in%20line.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hawaiian%20check%20in%20counter%20at%20JFK's%20Terminal%204.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564f302fd6200867dcfd73f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hawaiian%20check%20in%20counter%20at%20JFK's%20Terminal%204.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20checked%20two%20bags%2C%20both%20of%20which%20were%20well%20below%20the%2050-pound%20limit%20at%20about%2030%20pounds%20each.%20This%20gave%20us%20plenty%20of%20wiggle%20room%20to%20bring%20back%20souvenirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranted%2C%20we%20had%20to%20wait%2030%20minutes%20in%20Honolulu%20and%20an%20hour%20in%20New%20York%20on%20the%20return%20leg%20to%20collect%20our%20bags%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20to%20budget%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20breezed%20through%20security%20thanks%20to%20TSA%20PreCheck%20and%20spent%20about%20an%20hour%20at%20the%20Virgin%20Atlantic%20lounge.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224030%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20inside%20the%20lounge%20sitting%20and%20seats%20and%20at%20the%20bar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564f369fe5bc6545ebc9636%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222874%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lounge%20had%20plenty%20of%20seating%20with%20free%20food%20and%20drinks.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20the%20lounge%20came%20with%20our%20Priority%20Pass%20membership%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20best%20one%20available%20in%20Terminal%204%2C%20in%20my%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20boarded%20the%20aircraft%20about%2045%20minutes%20before%20departure%20and%20made%20our%20way%20to%20a%20pair%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20plane.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222975%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20blue%20pair%20of%20seats%20on%20Hawaiian.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564f3d3fd6200867dcfd7ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222495%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20seats%20onboard%20Hawaiian's%20Airbus%20A330.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHawaiian%20uses%20the%20widebody%20Airbus%20A330%20on%20its%20long-haul%20routes%20between%20Honolulu%20and%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20and%20it%20features%20dual%20se