%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20our%20honeymoon%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAbout%20two%20hours%20into%20the%20flight%2C%20we%20were%20served%20our%20first%20of%20two%20meals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20where%20Hawaiian%20shined%20over%20its%20US%20competitors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20pasta%20and%20meat%20sauce%20meal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564fca5fe5bc6545ebc9b9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20of%20two%20meals%20served%20on%20Hawaiian.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20food%20on%20Hawaiian%2C%20easily%20beating%20out%20Delta%20and%20United.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20offering%20was%20a%20pasta%20dish%2C%20and%20despite%20looking%20a%20little%20dry%2C%20it%20was%20surprisingly%20tasty.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20full%20meal%20with%20pasta%20and%20meat%20sauce%2C%20white%20wine%2C%20a%20cookie%2C%20and%20melon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564fcecfe5bc6545ebc9be9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20meal%20came%20with%20wine.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meal%20came%20with%20melon%20and%20a%20cookie%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20complimentary%20cup%20of%20wine.%20I'm%20not%20a%20huge%20wine%20drinker%2C%20but%20my%20husband%20enjoyed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20second%20meal%2C%20consisting%20of%20an%20egg%20sandwich%2C%20juice%2C%20and%20trail%20mix%2C%20was%20served%20about%2090%20minutes%20before%20landing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223754%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20bag%20with%20egg%20salad%2C%20trail%20mix%2C%20and%20juice.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564fd96c58b6f84123aa174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222822%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20see%20the%20difference%20in%20useable%20tray%20table%20space%20when%20the%20seat%20in%20front%20is%20not%20reclined.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20little%20bag%20it%20was%20served%20in%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20on-brand%20with%20the%20Hawaiian-inspired%20leisure%20theme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20thought%20Hawaiian's%20egg%20salad%20was%20particularly%20excellent.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holding%20her%20half-eaten%20egg%20sandwich.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564fdfffd6200867dcfde15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20combination%20of%20egg%20and%20cucumber%20was%20perfect.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20don't%20have%20the%20appetite%20for%20a%20second%20airline%20meal%20after%20traveling%20for%20hours%20on%20end.%20My%20stomach%20is%20just%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20loved%20the%20egg%20sandwich%20because%20it%20was%20simple%20and%20filling%20enough%20for%20an%20afternoon%20arrival%20in%20to%20Honolulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20the%20ride%20back%20to%20New%20York%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20we%20were%20met%20with%20the%20same%20standard%20economy%20seats%20and%20more%20good%20food.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20from%20the%20plane%20after%20takeoff%20with%20Diamond%20Head%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564fe4bfd6200867dcfde6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20from%20the%20plane%20after%20takeoff%20from%20Honolulu%20with%20Diamond%20Head%20in%20the%20background.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20flight%20was%20another%2010%20hours%20nonstop.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20it%20was%20a%20red-eye%2C%20and%20Hawaiian%20provided%20a%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20my%20seats%2C%20the%20aft%20pairs%20were%20taken%2C%20so%20we%20sat%20further%20up%20in%20row%2038.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20first%20meal%20was%20meatballs%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20veggies.%20Similar%20to%20the%20outbound%20meal%2C%20it%20was%20served%20with%20fruit%20and%20a%20pastry.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20meatball%20with%20rice%20and%20veggies%20dish%20served%20with%20fruit%20and%20a%20chocolate%20pastry.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564fee8fd6200867dcfdf54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20the%20fresh%20fruit.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20the%20meal%20looked%20questionable%20but%20was%20surprisingly%20flavorful%20and%20filling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20this%20was%20a%20red-eye%20flight%2C%20the%20second%20meal%20contained%20mostly%20breakfast%20food%2C%20including%20a%20muffin%2C%20orange%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20crackers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20muffin%2C%20orange%20juice%2C%20and%20orange.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564ff36fe5bc6545ebc9f01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20second%20meal%20served%20with%20orange%20juice.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20probably%20the%20least%20impressive%20meal%20of%20the%20bunch%2C%20but%20the%20orange%20and%20muffin%20were%20both%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20I%20again%20like%20the%20little%20bag%20it%20was%20served