the%20US%20is%20longer%20than%20some%20routes%20to%20Europe%2C%20but%20that's%20true%20of%20Hawaiian's%20New%20York%20to%20Honolulu%20nonstop.%20Its%20flight%20to%20and%20from%20Boston%20is%20actually%20even%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20that%20means%20travelers%20should%20prepare%20to%20sit%20for%2010%20hours%2C%20including%20bringing%20snacks%20in%20case%20airline%20food%20isn't%20your%20taste%2C%20drinking%20plenty%20of%20water%20before%20and%20during%20the%20flight%2C%20and%20carrying%20sleep%20aids%20like%20melatonin%20and%20an%20eye%20mask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-on-hawaiian-airlines-new-york-honolulu-review-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701165601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656504a8fe5bc6545ebca51a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-on-hawaiian-airlines-new-york-honolulu-review-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20ditched%20Delta%20to%20fly%20on%20Hawaiian%20for%20our%20honeymoon.%20I'd%20easily%20book%20again%20solely%20because%20the%20food%20was%20better%20than%20any%20other%20US%20carrier.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22trains%40insider.com%20(Taylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-on-hawaiian-airlines-new-york-honolulu-review-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Telangana%20Poll%20Date%20Nears%2C%20Parties%20Set%20Sights%20on%20the%20Muslim%20Vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28145637%2F33877013268_16c99d849f_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20the%20polling%20day%20(November%2030)%20approaches%20in%20Telangana%2C%20all%20political%20parties%2C%20except%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20have%20clearly%20set%20their%20sights%20on%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20that%20comprises%20around%2013%25%20of%20the%20electorate.%20Political%20rhetoric%20and%20declarations%20were%20carefully%20worded%20to%20woo%20the%20community.%20But%2C%20given%20the%20nature%20of%20statements%20of%20prominent%20Muslim%20organisations%20and%20influential%20clerics%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20who%20will%20overwhelmingly%20bag%20the%20Muslim%20vote.%20A%20fractured%20Muslim%20vote%20remains%20a%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20familiar%20with%20recent%20developments%20say%20that%20this%20is%20because%20the%20opinion%20of%20Muslims%20continues%20to%20be%20divided.%20To%20vote%20for%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20or%20the%20Congress%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-muslim-voters-dilemma-congress-brs%5C%22%3Eremains%20a%20key%20question%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20350px)%2085vw%2C%20350px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22289%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20a%20panel%20of%20well%20known%20Muslim%20clerics%2C%20which%20included%20Maulana%20Khalid%20Saifullah%20Rahmani%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20(AIMPLB)%20president%2C%20took%20cognisance%20of%20this%20very%20fact.%20An%20excerpt%20from%20a%20statement%20the%20panel%20released%20reads%20thus%3A%20%E2%80%9CUndoubtedly%2C%20on%20this%20occasion%20the%20scenario%20should%20be%20that%20the%20support%20for%20any%20party%20be%20based%20on%20consensus.%20Or%2C%20at%20least%20a%20decision%20should%20be%20based%20on%20the%20view%20of%20the%20large%20majority.%20But%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20ground%20realities%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20is%20divided.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20delicate%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20underscores%20the%20need%20to%20stop%20Muslim%20votes%20from%20being%20divided%2C%20and%20points%20out%20that%20it%20is%20on%20account%20of%20this%20possibility%20that%20the%20panel%20decided%20not%20to%20support%20any%20political%20party.%20Instead%2C%20it%20requested%20the%20members%20of%20the%20community%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20candidate%20who%20has%20secular%20credentials%2C%20one%20%E2%80%9Cwho%20is%20less%20harmful%20for%20the%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20fact%20that%20Maulana%20Khalid%20is%20the%20fifth%20president%20of%20the%20AIMPLB%2C%20he%20continues%20to%20remain%20an%20influential%20figure.%20Though%20a%20non-political%20figure%2C%20he%20enjoys%20the%20support%20of%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(MIM)%20president%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20who%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20led%20a%20delegation%20of%20clerics%2C%20including%20Maulana%20Khalid%2C%20to%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20camp%20office%20in%20Pragathi%20Bhavan%20to%20urge%20him%20to%20not%20support%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20example%2C%20the%20Jamaat-e-Islami%E2%80%99s%20Telangana%20chapter%20refrained%20from%20announcing%20their%20support%20to%20either%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20BRS.%20Instead%2C%20its%20political%20committee%20chose%20to%20support%20individual%20candidates%20contesting%20the%20119%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Telangana.%20Unlike%20their%20previous%20stance%2C%20the%20Jamaat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-assembly%2Fjamaat-e-islami-telangana-supports-69-congress-41-brs-candidates%2Farticle67561775.ece%5C%22%3Echose%20to%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%2070%20Congress%20candidates%2C%2040%20BRS%20candidates%2C%20and%20seven%20AIMIM%20candidates.%20This%20is%20a%20change%20in%20its%20approach.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20Jamaat%20supported%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20in%202018%2C%20after%20extensive%20deliberations%20and%20sharing%20concerns%20with%20the%20top%20party%20leadership%2C%20announced%20its%20support%20to%20the%20BRS%20%5Bthen%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20meetings%20which%20led%20to%20the%20announcement%2C%20there%20were%20internal%20differences%20between%20political%20committee%20members.%20Some%20wanted%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20openly%20support%20the%20BRS.%20But%20others%20felt%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20changing%2C%20and%20that%20the%20inroads%20Congress%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20making%20must%20not%20be%20ignored.%20Eventually%2C%20extensive%20consultations%20and%20ground%20surveys%20were%20done.%20They%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20non-partisan%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Jamaat%20member%20closely%20following%20the%20developments%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20example%2C%20Jamiat-i-Ulama%E2%80%99s%20two%20factions%20ended%20up%20throwing%20their%20weight%20behind%20the%20two%20contenders.%20While%20the%20Jamiat%E2%80%99s%20Maulana%20Arshad%20Madani%20faction%2C%20with%20its%20headquarters%20in%20Yakutpura%20in%20the%20Old%20City%2C%20endorsed%20the%20BRS%2C%20the%20Maulana%20Mahmood%20Madani%20faction%2C%20which%20operates%20from%20Amberpet%E2%80%99s%20Zam%20Zam%20Masjid%2C%20supported%20the%20Congress.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20latter%20was%20busy%20extensively%20touring%20many%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%2033%20districts%20to%20question%20CM%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20treatment%20of%20Muslims%2C%20especially%20those%20residing%20in%20districts%20other%20than%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fresurgent-congress-telangana-brs%5C%22%3ECan%20the%20Resurgent%20Congress%20Wrest%20Telangana%20from%20the%20BRS%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20constitute%20over%2050%20lakh%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20population.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20official%20figures%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Muslim%20voters%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%2040%20lakh.%20According%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20the%20concentration%20of%20Muslims%20is%20highest%20in%20composite%20districts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20Ranga%20Reddy%20and%20Nizamabad.%20Members%20of%20political%20parties%20believe%20that%20there%20are%20around%2030%20assembly%20constituencies%20where%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20sentiment%20is%20palpable.%20A%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20appears%20to%20be%20disenchanted%20with%20the%20BRS.%20For%20their%20part%2C%20the%20pink%20party%20did%20make%20impressive%20budgetary%20allocations%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20portion%20going%20to%20the%20over%20200%20minority%20residential%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20minority%20welfare%20schemes.%20During%20its%20tenure%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20once%20a%20riot-prone%20city%2C%20did%20not%20see%20any%20major%20communal%20clash.%20Several%20Muslims%20themselves%20have%20admitted%20that%20Telangana%20and%20Hyderabad%20are%20relatively%20much%20safer%20compared%20to%20states%20in%20North%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKCR%20has%20backed%20many%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20policies%2C%20including%20demonetisation%20and%20GST.%20The%20promised%2012%25%20reservations%20for%20Muslims%20has%20not%20materialised.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20there%20is%20a%20persistent%20perception%20among%20many%20Muslims%20that%20KCR%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-bjp-brs-and-the-truth-behind-the-conspiracy-theories%5C%22%3Esecret%20understanding%20with%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20perception%20is%20unlikely%20to%20fade.%20Many%20are%20talking%20in%20such%20terms%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammed%20Faiz%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20small%20businessman%20from%20Malakpet%2C%20an%20AIMIM%20stronghold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believe%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20remove%20the%20BJP%20from%20power%20is%20to%20support%20the%20Congress.%20This%20is%20likely%20because%20parliamentary%20elections%20are%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20mid-next%20year%2C%20shortly%20after%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20Given%20the%20differing%20opinions%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20the%20Muslim%20community%20will%20vote.%20The%20answer%20will%20be%20clear%20only%20on%20December%203%2C%20when%20votes%20will%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701164744000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28145637%2F33877013268_16c99d849f_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-poll-date-parties-sights-muslim-voters%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20opinion%20of%20Muslims%20continues%20to%20be%20divided.%20To%20vote%20for%20the%20ruling%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20or%20the%20Congress%20party%20remains%20a%20key%20question.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-poll-date-parties-sights-muslim-voters%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Railways%20Hasn't%20Commissioned%20New%20Kavach%20Lines%20This%20Year%3A%20Performance%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F28145254%2F13286908034_bb8f865649_h.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Indian%20Railways%20Performance%20Highlight%20report%20has%20noted%20that%20the%20railways%20has%20not%20commissioned%20any%20new%20lines%20with%20its%20safety%20system%20Kavach%20till%20October%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20April%E2%80%93October%20period%20last%20year%2C%2010%20km%20of%20such%20lines%20were%20commissioned%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Flogistics%2Fno-new-kavach-lines-commissioned-till-oct-31-railways-performance-report%2Farticle67579827.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2527Commissioning%2520of%2520Kavach%2520is%2520Nil%2Ckm%2520till%2520Oct%252031%252C%25202023%2527%26amp%3Btext%3DIndian%2520Railways%2520has%2520not%2520commissioned%2Cyear%252C%2520the%2520performance%2520report%2520mentions.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Business%20Line%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommissioning%20of%20Kavach%20is%20Nil%20till%20October%2031%2C%20compare(d)%20to%2010%20km%20last%20fiscal%20during%20same%20period%20and%20against%20the%20target%20of%20637%20km%20till%20Oct%2031%2C%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20performance%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKavach%20is%20an%20Automatic%20Train%20Protection%20(ATP)%20system%20created%20by%20the%20Research%20Design%20and%20Standards%20Organisation%20(RDSO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20no%20lines%20under%20Kavach%20were%20commissioned%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20new%20line%20setting%20up%20was%20186.65%20km%2C%20the%20doubling%20of%20lines%20was%201019.69%20km%2C%20and%20gauge%20conversion%20(from%20narrow%20to%20broad%20gauge)%20was%2096%20km.%20A%20cumulative%20of%201302.34%20km%20was%20covered%20till%20Oct-end%2C%20at%20least%2025%20per%20cent-odd%20lesser%20than%20last%20year%20(across%20these%20categories)%20which%20covered%201728.55%20km%20(%20that%20included%20new%20line%20laying%20of%2052