e58_uttarakhand-tunnel-ambulance-_625x300_28_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-live-41-ambulances-lined-up-outside-tunnel-to-take-workers-to-hospital-4613267%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Forty-one%20ambulances%20remain%20on%20standby%20at%20the%20collapsed%20Silkyara%20tunnel's%20entrance%2C%20ready%20to%20whisk%20the%20workers%20away%20to%20the%20nearest%20medical%20facility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-live-41-ambulances-lined-up-outside-tunnel-to-take-workers-to-hospital-4613267%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-live-41-ambulances-lined-up-outside-tunnel-to-take-workers-to-hospital-4613267%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-rescue-op-live-41-ambulances-lined-up-outside-tunnel-to-take-workers-to-hospital-4613267%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Rat-Hole%20Mining%2C%20Outlawed%2C%20Saved%2041%20Trapped%20In%20Uttarkashi%20Tunnel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20mining%20practice%20banned%20for%20being%20unsafe%20has%20come%20to%20the%20aid%20of%20the%2041%20workers%20trapped%20inside%20an%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20after%20high-tech%2C%20imported%20machines%20broke%20down%20during%20the%20long-drawn%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERat-hole%20mining%20to%20rescue%20the%20trapped%20workers%20began%20yesterday%20after%20a%2025-tonne%20auger%20machine%20failed%20in%20the%20last%20leg%20of%20the%20challenging%20operation.%20This%20method%20of%20manual%20drilling%20has%20made%20quick%20progress%20and%20the%20diggers%20are%20now%20metres%20away%20from%20the%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20confined%20for%2017%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Rat-Hole%20Mining%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERat-hole%20mining%20is%20a%20method%20of%20extracting%20coal%20by%20digging%20very%20small%20pits%2C%20not%20more%20than%204%20feet%20wide.%20Once%20the%20miners%20reach%20the%20coal%20seam%2C%20tunnels%20are%20made%20sideways%20to%20extract%20the%20coal.%20The%20coal%20brought%20out%20is%20dumped%20nearby%20and%20later%20transported%20via%20highways.%20In%20rat-hole%20mining%2C%20workers%20enter%20the%20mines%20and%20use%20hand-held%20tools%20to%20dig.%20This%20is%20the%20most%20common%20method%20of%20mining%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20where%20the%20coal%20seam%20is%20very%20thin%20and%20any%20other%20method%20risks%20being%20economically%20unviable.%20The%20small%20size%20of%20the%20tunnels%20make%20children%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20the%20hazardous%20job%2C%20and%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20limited%20options%20for%20livelihood%2C%20many%20line%20up%20for%20the%20risky%20job.%20Many%20children%20also%20pose%20as%20adults%20to%20get%20work%20in%20such%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Was%20Rat-Hole%20Mining%20Banned%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20banned%20rat-hole%20mining%20in%202014%20for%20being%20unscientific%2C%20but%20the%20practice%20continues%20to%20be%20rampant.%20Several%20accidents%20have%20resulted%20in%20deaths%20of%20rat-hole%20miners%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state.%20In%202018%2C%2015%20men%20involved%20in%20illegal%20mining%20were%20trapped%20inside%20a%20flooded%20mine.%20Only%20two%20bodies%20could%20be%20recovered%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20rescue%20operation%20that%20lasted%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months.%20Another%20such%20accident%20took%20place%20in%202021%20when%20five%20miners%20were%20trapped%20in%20a%20flooded%20mine.%20Three%20bodies%20were%20found%20before%20rescue%20teams%20called%20off%20the%20operation%20after%20a%20month.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20environmental%20pollution%20caused%20by%20this%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMining%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20key%20source%20of%20revenue%20for%20the%20state%20government.%20The%20Manipur%20government%20has%20challenged%20the%20NGT%20ban%2C%20arguing%20that%20there%20is%20no%20other%20feasible%20mining%20option%20for%20the%20region.%20A%20panel%20appointed%20by%20Meghalaya%20High%20Court%20in%202022%20found%20rat-hole%20mining%20continues%20unabated%20in%20Meghalaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Uttarakhand%20Operation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outlawed%20practice%20has%20now%20come%20to%20the%20rescue%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20after%20an%20American%20auger%20machine%20failed%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20debris%20blocking%20their%20escape.%20Two%20teams%20of%20specialists%2C%20a%20total%20of%2012%20men%2C%20have%20been%20flown%20in%20from%20Delhi%20for%20this%20task.%20The%20Uttarakhand%20government's%20nodal%20officer%20Neeraj%20Khairwal%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20the%20men%20brought%20in%20were%20not%20rat-hole%20miners%20but%20experts%20in%20the%20technique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajput%20Rai%2C%20one%20of%20the%20experts%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20one%20man%20does%20the%20drilling%2C%20another%20collects%20the%20rubble%20and%20the%20third%20places%20it%20on%20a%20trolley%20to%20be%20pulled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20specialists%20have%20been%20at%20work%20inside%20the%20800%20mm%20pipe%20to%20remove%20the%20debris%20manually%20using%20hand-held%20tools.%20One%20of%20the%20specialists%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20yesterday%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20shovel%20and%20other%20specialist%20tools%20will%20be%20used.%20For%20oxygen%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20blower%20with%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20form%20of%20drilling%20is%20a%20tiring%20task%2C%20and%20the%20diggers%20are%20taking%20turns.%20According%20to%20rescue%20teams%2C%20these%20professionals%20are%20skilled%20in%20cutting%20through%20metal%20barriers%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701161700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com