%20founder%20of%20the%20DevTernity%20Conference%20(not%20pictured)%2C%20Eduards%20Sizovs%20said%20on%20X%20that%20the%20profiles%20weren't%20an%20attempt%20to%20bolster%20the%20event's%20diversity.%20%3Cp%3Egorodenkoff%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20tech%20conference%20organizer%20was%20accused%20of%20listing%20fake%20female%20panelists%20on%20his%20event%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEduards%20Sizovs%20said%20two%20panelists%20had%20dropped%20out%20earlier%20while%20the%20last%20one%20was%20a%20placeholder.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20apologized%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20bad%20administration%20slip-up%20on%20his%20part.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20online%20software%20development%20conference%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20after%20its%20organizers%20were%20accused%20of%20listing%20fake%20female%20panelists%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20DevTernity%20Conference%20was%20slated%20to%20run%20from%207%20to%208%20December%2C%20and%20featured%20speakers%20from%20Microsoft%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevternity.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevent%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tickets%20have%20been%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGergely%20Orosz%2C%20author%20of%20the%20tech-focused%20newsletter%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pragmatic%20Engineer%26quot%3B%20pointed%20out%20the%20fake%20speaker%20profiles%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGergelyOrosz%2Fstatus%2F1728177708608450705%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20series%20of%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20on%20November%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20bought%20tickets%20to%20DevTernity%20(%26quot%3BDevTernity%26quot%3B)%20on%207-8%20Dec%20you've%20been%20duped%20with%20fake%20speaker%20Anna%20Boyle%20who%20is%20still%20on%20the%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20Orosz%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BA%20made%20up%20profile%2C%20AI%20image%2C%20no%20such%20staff%20eng%20at%20Coinbase.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conference's%20founder%2C%20Eduards%20Sizovs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feduardsi%2Fstatus%2F1728422017417032140%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresponded%20to%20Orosz's%20accusations%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20same%20day.%20Sizovs%20apologized%20for%20the%20confusion%20caused.%20He%20also%20explained%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20three%20fake%20female%20profiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sizovs%2C%20he%20secured%20the%20participation%20of%20two%20female%20panelists%2C%20but%20both%20eventually%20withdrew%20their%20participation.%20Sizovs%20admitted%20that%20he%20had%20left%20both%20speaker%20profiles%20up%20on%20the%20website%20while%20he%20continued%20searching%20for%20replacement%20speakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20last%20profile%2C%20Sizovs%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdemo%20persona%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Bauto-generated%2C%20with%20a%20random%20title%2C%20random%20Twitter%20handle%2C%20random%20picture.%26quot%3B%20The%20profile%20has%20since%20been%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESizovs%20said%20that%20the%20profiles%20weren't%20an%20attempt%20at%20bolstering%20the%20event's%20diversity%20but%20were%20a%20bad%20administration%20slip-up%20on%20his%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20noticed%20the%20issue%20in%20October%2C%20but%20my%20busy%20mind%20suggested%20delaying%20the%20fix%20until%20we%20finalize%20the%20program%20because%201)%20it%20was%20not%20a%20quick%20fix%202)%20it's%20better%20to%20have%20that%20demo%20persona%20while%20I%20am%20searching%20for%20the%20replacement%20speakers%2C%203)%20and%20the%20persona%20isn't%20part%20of%20the%20schedule%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20Sizovs%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20can%20wait%2C%20no%20harm%2C%20only%20good%20intentions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20seems%20like%20this%20%26quot%3Bissue%26quot%3B%20might%20already%20be%20h