ks%20is%20a%20retrograde%20step%20in%20promoting%20cultural%20harmony%2C%20unity%20and%20peace%2C%20and%20has%20no%20merit%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20must%20understand%20that%20in%20order%20to%20be%20a%20patriot%2C%20one%20need%20not%20be%20inimical%20to%20those%20from%20abroad%20especially%2C%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20true%20patriot%20is%20a%20person%20who%20is%20selfless%2C%20who%20is%20devoted%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20country%2C%20which%20he%20cannot%20be%20unless%20he%20is%20a%20person%20who%20is%20good%20at%20heart.%20A%20person%20who%20is%20good%20at%20heart%20would%20welcome%20in%20his%20country%20any%20activity%20which%20promotes%20peace%2C%20harmony%2C%20and%20tranquillity%20within%20the%20country%20and%20across%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArts%2C%20music%2C%20sports%2C%20culture%2C%20dance%20and%20so%20on%20are%20the%20activities%20which%20rise%20above%20nationalities%2C%20cultures%20and%20nations%2C%20and%20truly%20bring%20about%20peace%2C%20tranquillity%2C%20unity%20and%20harmony%20in%20nation%20and%20between%20nations%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20Pakistan%20was%20a%20participant.%20This%20happened%20only%20because%20of%20appreciable%20positive%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20overall%20peace%20and%20harmony%20in%20consonance%20with%20Article%2051%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20which%20is%20about%20promotion%20of%20international%20peace%20and%20security%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701158160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22h