ical%20College%2C%20fulfilling%20an%20internship%20requirement%20to%20meet%20curriculum%20obligations%20before%20his%20anticipated%20graduation%20in%20June%20of%20the%20following%20year.%20His%20role%20involved%20serving%20as%20an%20online%20game%20streamer%20for%20Henan%20Qinyi%20Culture%20and%20Media%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20incident%20occurred%20on%20November%2010%20in%20Li's%20rented%20house%20in%20Zhengzhou%2C%20Henan%20province.%20Roommates%20discovered%20him%20breathing%20rapidly%20and%20unresponsive%20during%20sleep%2C%20prompting%20them%20to%20seek%20emergency%20assistance.%20Despite%20their%20efforts%2C%20Li%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20upon%20arrival%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcooperation%20agreement%26quot%3B%20obtained%20by%20the%20newspaper%2C%20Li%20was%20obligated%20to%20livestream%20for%20240%20hours%20in%2026%20days%20and%20upload%2015%20short%20videos%20each%20month%20to%20earn%20a%20minimum%20salary%20of%203%2C000%20yuan.%20Li%20had%20worked%20the%20day%20shift%20since%20October%20but%20transitioned%20to%20the%20night%20shift%20on%20November%205%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fa%2F202311%2F20%2FWS655b34e7a31090682a5ef228.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EChina%20Daily%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20engaged%20in%20live-streaming%20sessions%20from%209%20pm%20to%206%20am%20for%20five%20consecutive%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecords%20indicate%20that%20Li%20conducted%2089%20live-streaming%20sessions%20between%20October%2015%20and%20November%2010%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3242427%2Fgames-death-online-anger-family-china-student-who-died-after-marathon-live-stream-gaming-sessions%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELi's%20father%20revealed%20that%20the%20company%20requested%20the%20shift%20change%20due%20to%20better%20tips%20and%20higher%20earnings.%20However%2C%20Li%20was%20reportedly%20unhappy%20with%20the%20new%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20represented%20legally%20by%20Zhang%2C%20denied%20all%20responsibility%2C%20emphasizing%20a%20cooperative%20agreement%20with%20Li.%20%26quot%3BWe%20provide%20a%20venue%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20stated%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20only%20take%20a%20commission%20from%20viewer%20gifts%20given%20to%20the%20live-streamer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhang%20acknowledged%20the%20challenges%20many%20live-streamers%20face%20in%20managing%20the%20extent%20of%20their%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20compensation%2C%20the%20employer%20has%20offered%205%2C000%20yuan%20or%20Rs%2058%2C750%20to%20Li's%20family.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20is%20now%20facing%20public%20outrage%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20for%20its%20perceived%20irresponsible%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701157980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp323p768_online-gaming-_625x300_28_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-chinese-student-dies-live-streaming-gaming-sessions-for-5-days-4613058%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unfortunate%20incident%20occurred%20on%20November%2010%20in%20Li's%20rented%20house%20in%20Zhengzhou%2C%20Henan%20province.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-chinese-student-dies-live-streaming-gaming-sessions-for-5-days-4613058%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-chinese-student-dies-live-streaming-gaming-sessions-for-5-days-4613058%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Foverworked-chinese-student-dies-live-streaming-gaming-sessions-for-5-days-4613058%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20undergoing%20Agniveer%