dam-zampa-return-home-ahead-of-3rd-t20i-vs-india-4-more-players-to-fly-soon-4612906%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCompletely%20Illegal%26quot%3B%3A%20Probe%20Agency%20Summons%20To%205%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Officers%20Paused%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Madras%20High%20Court%20today%20stayed%20the%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20to%20five%20district%20collectors%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20connection%20with%20alleged%20illegal%20sand%20mining%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stayed%20the%20summons%20for%20three%20weeks%3B%20however%2C%20it%20did%20not%20stay%20the%20ED%20investigation%20as%20prayed%20for%20by%20the%20ruling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20government%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20collectors%20and%20the%20state%20government%20must%20respond%20to%20the%20ED's%20queries%20within%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-judge%20Madras%20High%20Court%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20SS%20Sundar%20and%20Sundar%20Mohany%20yesterday%20deferred%20their%20decision%20until%20November%2028%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20state%20Public%20Department%20Secretary%20K%20Nanthakumar%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Collectors%20of%20Ariyalur%2C%20Vellore%2C%20Thanjavur%2C%20Karur%2C%20and%20Tiruchirapalli%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20sought%20to%20invalidate%20probe%20agency%20ED's%20summons%2C%20which%20mandated%20the%20collectors'%20personal%20presence%20on%20various%20dates%20to%20furnish%20details%20about%20sand%20mining%20operations%20within%20their%20respective%20jurisdictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20issued%20the%20summons%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Nanthakumar%20argued%20that%20the%20ED%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20conducting%20an%20investigation%2C%20has%20embarked%20on%20an%20extensive%20and%20arbitrary%20practice%20of%20issuing%20summons%20to%20district%20collectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Government's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20ED%20doesn't%20have%20such%20unbridled%20powers%20and%20that%20its%20summons%20to%20collectors%20is%20against%20the%20spirit%20of%20federalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20it%20has%20filed%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20in%20illegal%20sand%20mining%20cases%20and%20that%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20provide%20details%2C%20it%20argued%20that%20the%20central%20agency%20should%20seek%20details%20only%20through%20the%20state%20government%20and%20that%20any%20investigation%20should%20be%20conducted%20with%20its%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20DMK%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20misusing%20central%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20ED%2C%20to%20target%20political%20opponents%20in%20opposition-ruled%20states.%20They%20also%20point%20to%20the%20negligible%20conviction%20rate%20in%20ED%20cases.%20When%20those%20targeted%20decide%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20DMK%20claims%20they%20become%20%26quot%3Bwhitewashed%20saints%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20allegation%20the%20BJP%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EED's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20survey%20by%20an%20expert%20from%20an%20IIT%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20claimed%20that%20illegal%20sand%20mining%20worth%20Rs%204%2C500%20crore%20had%20taken%20place%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20that%20the%20proceeds%20were%20laundered.%20It%20claimed%20that%20it%20had%20the%20power%20to%20summon%20collectors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20has%20argued%20that%20it%20can%20summon%20both%20private%20individuals%20and%20government%20officials%20as%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20gives%20it%20the%20power%20to%20summon%20anyone%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A