3EAbby%20said%20that%20the%20confrontation%20began%20when%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20Ayurveda%20group%20Patanjali%20and%20its%20leader%20Baba%20Ramdev.%20He%20alleged%20that%20Vijay%20Patel%20responded%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20scientifically%20or%20rationally%2C%20but%20using%20communalism%20and%20hurling%20religious%20slurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Patel%20tweeted%20calling%20Abby%20a%20%E2%80%98propaganda%20doctor%E2%80%99%20who%20always%20targets%20Ayurveda%20and%20Yoga%20%E2%80%98because%20he%20belongs%20to%20the%20missionary%20cartel%20which%20uses%20the%20modern%20medical%20field%20as%20their%20conversion%20factory%E2%80%99.%20Vijay%20Patel%20then%20asked%20people%20if%20they%20want%20to%20know%20Abby%20and%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Vijay%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Dr%20Abby%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmassive%20right-wing%20Hindu%20nationalist%20social%20media%20abusive%20machinery%E2%80%9D%20targeted%20him%2C%20inundating%20his%20posts%20with%20abuse%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20vulgar%20comments.%20He%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20posted%20on%20matters%20of%20medical%20science%20and%20medical%20education%20simplified%20for%20the%20people.%20It%20is%20my%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20having%20taken%20the%20legal%20action%2C%20he%20expressed%20his%20faith%20in%20the%20Kerala%20Police%20Department%2C%20the%20Kochi%20City%20Police%2C%20and%20the%20State%20Cyber%20Cell.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20faith%20that%20they%20will%20hunt%20this%20man%20down%20and%20bring%20him%20what%20he%20deserves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Abby%20Philips%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20controversy%2C%20having%20received%20approximately%2015%20legal%20notices%20over%20the%20years.%20He%20is%20known%20for%20