aMoitra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMahuaMoitra%2Fstatus%2F1728426379501592815%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%E2%80%99s%20post%20has%20come%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Lokpal%20referring%20her%20case%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20for%20investigation%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fthey-want-me-to-shut-up-and-i-am-not-shutting-up-mahua-moitra-on-cash-for-query-allegations%2Fcid%2F1976109%5C%22%3Ecash-for-query%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20TMC%20MP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20response%20dated%20November%203%2C%20the%20anti-corruption%20ombudsman%20has%20not%20had%20a%20chairman%20after%20Justice%20Pinaki%20Chandra%20Ghose%20left%20the%20post%20in%20May%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGhose%20was%20the%20first%20and%20only%20chairperson%20the%20Lokpal%20has%20had%20since%20the%20body%20was%20constituted%20in%202014.%20Justice%20Pradip%20Kumar%20Mohanty%2C%20a%20judicial%20member%20of%20Lokpal%2C%20is%20currently%20the%20acting%20chairperson.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-treatment-of-mahua-moitra-is-a-case-study-on-gender-power-and-politics-in-india%5C%22%3EThe%20Treatment%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Is%20a%20Case%20Study%20on%20Gender%2C%20Power%20and%20Politics%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RTI%20also%20showed%20that%20three%20out%20of%20eight%20member%20posts%20are%20vacant.%20In%20March%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Lokpal%20was%20criticised%20by%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%20for%20its%20non-performance%20and%20failure%20to%20fill%20the%20post%20of%20chairperson%20and%20other%20members%2C%20the%20%3