20(WHO)%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F28%2Fgender-based-violence-1-in-3-women-faces-physical-or-sexual-harassment-in-her-lifetime-says-who-2636849.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20estimates%2C%20that%20around%2033%25%20of%20women%20worldwide%20experience%20physical%20or%20sexual%20violence%2C%20and%20the%20South-East%20Asia%20Region%20(SEARO)%20is%20the%20second-highest%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWHO%20SEARO%20regional%20director%20Poonam%20Khetrapal%20Singh%20told%20the%20daily%20that%20most%20women%20are%20at%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20being%20abused%20by%20the%20people%20they%20live%20with.%20Most%20of%20this%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20intimate%20partner%20violence%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20against%20women%2C%20especially%20intimate%20partner%20violence%2C%20has%20serious%20health%20impacts%2C%20both%20immediate%20and%20long%20term.%20These%20encompass%20injuries%20as%20well%20as%20serious%20physical%2C%20mental%2C%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarking%20the%20start%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fen%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fending-violence-against-women%2Funite%2F16-days-of-activism%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9816%20Days%20of%20Activism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20%E2%80%98gender-based%20violence%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20said%20violence%20against%20women%20is%20preventable.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20rooted%20in%20gender%20inequality%20and%20harmful%20gender%20norms%20that%20make%20violence%20against%20women%20acceptable.%20In%20particular%2C%20evidence%20shows%20that%20intimate%20partner%20violence%20and%20sexual%20violence%20result%20from%20factors%20occurring%20at%20individual%2C%20family%2C%20community%20and%20wider%20society%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%20as%20well%2C%20WHO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F09-03-2021-devastatingly-pervasive-1-in-3-women-globally-experience-violence%5C%22%3Ehad%20released%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20similar%20report%20highlighting%20the%20same%20numbers.%20It%20had%20said%20that%20the%20number%20has%20remained%20largely%20unchanged%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20COVID-19%2C%20violence%20against%20women%20cannot%20be%20stopped%20with%20a%20vaccine.%20We%20can%20only%20fight%20it%20with%20deep-rooted%20and%20sustained%20efforts%20%E2%80%93%20by%20governments%2C%20communities%20and%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20to%20change%20harmful%20attitudes%2C%20improve%20access%20to%20opportunities%20and%20services%20for%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20and%20foster%20healthy%20and%20mutually%20respectful%20relationships%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tedros%20Adhanom%20Ghebreyesus%2C%20WHO%20Director-General%2C%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fmanipur-sexual-violence-bjp-apathy-patriarchy%5C%22%3EWhy%20Does%20Our%20Government%20Need%20a%20Graphic%20Depiction%20of%20Violence%20Against%20Women%20to%20Act%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantifying%20the%20impact%20of%20gender%20violence%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20trauma%20women%20endure%2C%20can%20be%20difficult.%20Such%20experiences%20may%20occur%20either%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%20or%20intermittently.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20impact%20of%20violence%20could%20go%20beyond%20physical%20and%20mental%20their%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20experiencing%20gender%20violence%20often%20incurs%20higher%20costs%2C%20including%20medical%20expenses%2C%20emotional%20well-being%2C%20and%20disruptions%20to%20education%20or%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20UN%20Women%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fstories%2F2016%2F9%2Fspeech-by-lakshmi-puri-on-economic-costs-of-violence-against-women%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016%2C%20women%20who%20experience%20violence%20earn%2060%25%20lower%20than%20women%20who%20do%20not%20experience%20such%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20citing%20research%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20cost%20of%20violence%20against%20women%20could%20amount%20to%20around%202%25%20of%20the%20global%20gross%20domestic%20product%20(GDP).%20This%20is%20equivalent%20to%201.5%20trillion%2C%20approximately%2C%20the%20size%20of%20the%20economy%20of%20Canada.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20could%20increase%20its%20GDP%20by%20%24770%20billion%20by%202025%20by%20getting%20more%20women%20to%20work%20and%20increasing%20equality%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Ffeatured-insights%2Fgender-equality%2Fthe-power-of-parity-advancing-womens-equality-in-india-2018%5C%22%3Esaid%20McKinsey%20Global%20Institute%20in%202018.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Yet%2C%20only%2027%25%20of%20Indian%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fcurrent-affairs%2Frising-income-stability-linked-to-declining-working-females-in-india-117050400150_1.html%5C%22%3Eare%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Center%20for%20Monitoring%20the%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%20found%20that%20only%2010%25%20of%20working-age%20Indian%20women%20in%202022%20were%20either%20employed%20or%20looking%20for%20jobs%2C%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fgallery%2F2023%2F4%2F10%2Fas-indias-population-soars-number-of-women-in-workforce-shrinks%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%202023.%20That%20means%20only%2039%20million%20women%20are%20employed%20in%20the%20workforce%20compared%20with%20361%20million%20men%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701151198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28111747%2Fimage-1551.png%22%2C%22orig