0Elon%20Musk%20recently%20expressed%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20with%20Hamas%20after%20receiving%20a%20symbolic%20dog%20tag%20from%20a%20father%20whose%20child%20was%20allegedly%20held%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20in%20Gaza.%20Mr%20Musk%20arrived%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20on%20Monday%20for%20a%20two-day%20visit.%20During%20a%20meeting%20with%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20and%20the%20families%20of%20hostages%2C%20a%20parent%20named%20Malki%20presented%20the%20tech%20mogul%20with%20a%20dog%20tag%20with%20%26quot%3Bour%20hearts%20are%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%26quot%3B%20engraved%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20the%20Israeli%20president's%20office%20shared%20a%20video%20of%20Mr%20Musk%20meeting%20the%20families%20of%20the%20hostages.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20meeting%20President%20%40Isaac_Herzog%20held%20with%20%40ElonMusk%20%26amp%3B%20families%20of%20hostages%2C%20Rachel%20showed%20Elon%20a%20video%20of%20her%20son%20Hersh%2C%20badly%20injured%2C%20being%20abducted%20by%20Hamas.%20Malki%2C%20father%20of%20another%20hostage%2C%20Omer%2C%20presented%20Elon%20with%20a%20dog-tag%20inscribed%20%26quot%3Bour%20hearts%20are%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20caption%20of%20the%20post%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%2C%20the%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20CEO%20vowed%20to%20wear%20the%20dog%20tag%20every%20day%20until%20all%20hostages%20are%20released%20by%20Hamas.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20wear%20it%20every%20day%20until%20your%20loved%20ones%20are%20released%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tweeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20a%20look%20below%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20will%20wear%20it%20every%20day%20until%20your%20loved%20ones%20are%20released%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2