%20the%20recently%20concluded%20cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20have%20appealed%20to%20the%20authorities%20to%20drop%20the%20charges%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Syed%20Mohammad%20Qasim%20Bukhari%2C%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20students%20said%20that%20his%20son%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20any%20criminal%20activity%20in%20the%20past%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20toiled%20hard%20for%20his%20education.%20What%20has%20happened%20is%20unfortunate%20but%20I%20refuse%20to%20believe%20that%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20any%20anti-national%20activity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasim%E2%80%99s%20son%20is%20a%20fourth%20semester%20student%20of%20Bachelors%20in%20Veterinary%20Science%20at%20the%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20University%20of%20Agriculture%20Science%20and%20Technology%20where%2C%20on%20November%2019%2C%20Kashmiri%20students%20allegedly%20celebrated%20after%20India%20lost%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20finals.%20The%20family%20lives%20in%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Baramulla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20should%20drop%20the%20charges%20against%20his%20son%20and%20other%20students%20so%20that%20they%20can%20continue%20their%20education%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20not%20put%20the%20careers%20of%20students%20at%20stake.%20If%20they%20have%20committed%20any%20wrong%2C%20I%20apologise%20on%20their%20behalf%20and%20appeal%20the%20authorities%20to%20set%20him%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20the%20celebrations%20were%20allegedly%20reported%20from%20one%20of%20the%20two%20undergraduate%20hostels%20of%20the%20university.%20The%20complainant%2C%20Sachin%20Bains%2C%20a%20student%20from%20Punjab%2C%20stated%20that%20there%20was%20purported%20sloganeering%20inside%20the%20hostel%2C%20where%20some%20local%20students%20stay%2C%20and%20he%20was%20allegedly%20abused%20and%20threatened%20by%20Kashmiri%20students%20purportedly%20over%20rooting%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20complaint%2C%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20was%20filed%20by%20Ganderbal%20police%20station%20under%20Section%2013%20(%20advocating%2C%20abetting%20or%20inciting%20any%20unlawful%20activity)%20of%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA)%20and%20Sections%20505%20(inciting%20communal%20violence)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%20and%20seven%20Kashmiri%20students%20named%20in%20the%20complain%20were%20arrested%20under%20anti-terror%20law%20among%20other%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20court%20in%20central%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Ganderbal%20has%20sent%20the%20seven%20suspects%20to%20police%20remand%20till%20November%2030%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20family%20member%20of%20a%20second%20student%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named%2C%20also%20urged%20the%20authorities%20to%20drop%20the%20anti-terror%20charges%20against%20their%20kin%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20he%20has%20committed%20a%20wrong%2C%20charging%20him%20for%20terrorism%20is%20injustice.%20His%20career%20will%20be%20ruined.%20I%20beg%20the%20authorities%20to%20give%20him%20a%20second%20chance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20family%20member%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%20at%20the%20university%2C%20three%20among%20those%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%20are%20orphans%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20students%2C%20Mohsin%20Farooq%2C%20returned%20from%20Thailand%20recently%20where%20he%20was%20sent%20on%20a%20three-month%20research%20trip%20for%20his%20exceptional%20academic%20achievements%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Shafeeq%20Bhat%2C%20who%20represents%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20students%2C%20said%20that%20they%20are%20preparing%20a%20legal%20defence%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20(students)%20are%20all%20nationalists%20like%20other%20students%20at%20the%20college.%20None%20of%20them%20has%20been%20indicted%20in%20any%20crime%20and%20most%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20economically%20backward%20sections%20of%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Jeeve%20Jeeve%20Pakistan%E2%80%99%20created%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%3A%20FIR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sachin%20told%20the%20police%20that%20the%20students%20shouted%20pro-Pakistan%20slogans%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Jeeve%20Jeeve%20Pakistan%E2%80%99%20which%20created%20an%20%E2%80%9Catmosphere%20of%20fear%E2%80%9D%20among%20the%20non-local%20students%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperintendent%20of%20Police%20Nikhil%20Borkar%20Ganderbal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1059698%2Fseven-kashmiri-students-arrested-after-row-over-celebrating-indias-world-cup-loss%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Csome%20sections%20are%20added%20or%20deleted%20depending%20upon%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20investigation.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CThe%20investigation%20is%20on%20and%20whatever%20will%20be%20there%2C%20we%20will%20let%20you%20know%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Borkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDisconcerting%20%26amp%3B%20shocking%20that%20cheering%20for%20a%20winning%20team%20too%20has%20been%20criminalised%20in%20Kashmir.%20Normalising%20slapping%20of%20draconian%20laws%20like%20UAPA%20on%20journalists%2C%20activists%20%26amp%3B%20now%20students%20reveals%20the%20ruthless%20mindset%20of%20the%20establishment%20towards%20youngsters%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20Hearts%20%26amp%3B%20minds%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGtOHr9KI7O%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FGtOHr9KI7O%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20(%40MehboobaMufti)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMehboobaMufti%2Fstatus%2F1729368767195734361%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20have%20invoked%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20against%20people%20in%20Kashmir%20for%20hosting%20celebrations%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20cricket%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20police%20filed%20a%20case%20over%20the%20%E2%80%98celebration%E2%80%99%20of%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%E2%80%99s%20victory%20against%20India%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20October%202021%20at%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Srinagar%20under%20Sections%20105%20(A)%20and%20505%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Section%2013%20of%20the%20UAPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20registered%20after%20some%20students%20and%20doctors%2C%20who%20were%20putting%20up%20in%20a%20hostel%20of%20Sher-I-Kashmir%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%2C%20allegedly%20raised%20slogans%20and%20burst%20firecrackers%20to%20celebrate%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20cricket%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20three%20Kashmiri%20students%20were%20booked%20in%20Agra%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20under%20Sections%20124-A%20(sedition)%2C%20Section%20153-A%20(enmity%20between%20communities)%2C%20505-(1)%20(B)%20(intent%20to%20cause%20fear%20or%20alarm%20to%20the%20public)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%2066-F%20(cyber-terrorism)%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20Police%20had%20said%20that%20the%20students%2C%20who%20were%20enrolled%20at%20Raja%20Balwant%20Singh%20Engineering%20College%20under%20a%20centrally-sponsored%20scholarship%20scheme%2C%20had%20allegedly%20celebrated%20India%E2%80%99s%20loss%20to%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20T-20%20cricket%20match%20and%20sent%20WhatsApp%20messages%20%E2%80%9Cagainst%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20widespread%20celebrations%20had%20erupted%20in%20Kashmir%20parts%20after%20Pakistan%20defeated%20India%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%20at%20the%20Oval%20with%20the%20late%20Hurriyat%20hawk%20Syed%20Ali%20Geelani%20and%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chairman%20Mirwaiz%20Omar%20Farooq%20congratulating%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20for%20clinching%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20a%20fracas%20broke%20out%20at%20the%20prestigious%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20involving%20Kashmiri%20and%20non-local%20students%20following%20India%E2%80%99s%20loss%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20to%20West%20Indies.%20Some%20Kashmiri%20students%20and%20a%20local%20courier%20boy%20were%20beaten%20up%20by%20non-local%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20had%20triggered%20protests%20at%20the%20institute%20with%20the%20non-local%20students%20demanding%20that%20the%20campus%20should%20be%20shifted%20out%20of%20Kashmir%20while%20their%20Kashmiri%20students%20were%20allegedly%20roughed%20up%20by%20police%2C%20prompting%20the%20authorities%20to%20shut%20down%20the%20institute%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701148852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F28104743%2FF_SqDC5aIAAi4ou.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmir-students-arrested-uapa-pakistan-india-cricket%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20have%20invoked%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20against%20people%20in%20Kashmir%20for%20hosting%20celebrations%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20cricket%20matches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fkashmir-students-arrested-uapa-pakistan-india-cricket%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Imran%20Khan%20to%20be%20produce