20on%20Bali%20Island%20comprising%2015%20villages%20under%20the%20Gosaba%20community%20block%20with%20a%20population%20of%20around%2037%2C000.%20Located%20just%20outside%20the%20Sundarban%20tiger%20reserve%2C%20it%20is%20the%20entry%20point%20for%20tourists%20visiting%20the%20Sundarban%20delta%2C%20known%20for%20its%20distinctive%20mangroves%2C%20diverse%20flora%20and%20fauna%2C%20and%20bird%20sanctuaries.%20However%2C%20Bali%20Island%20lacks%20bustle.%20While%20there%20are%20a%20handful%20of%20eco-resorts%2C%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20the%20island%E2%80%99s%20inhabitants%20are%20primarily%20rooted%20in%20rain-fed%20agriculture%2C%20fisheries%2C%20honey%20collection%2C%20and%20activities%20such%20as%20fishing%20and%20catching%20crabs.%20The%20island%20is%20cut%20off%20from%20the%20mainland%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20remains%20entirely%20isolated%2C%20with%20no%20road%20or%20alternative%20means%20of%20connectivity%20apart%20from%20water%20transport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStories%20like%20Tumpa%E2%80%99s%20are%20common%20in%20almost%20every%20village%2C%20involving%20both%20girls%20and%20sometimes%20boys.%20In%20an%20area%20already%20struggling%20with%20widespread%20poverty%2C%20the%20unmonitored%20riverine%20expanses%20of%20the%20Sundarban%20and%20surroundings%20have%20become%20happy%20hunting%20grounds%20for%20traffickers.%20Local%20activist%20Soumitra%20Mondal%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20%E2%80%98Nonadwiper%20Pathshala%E2%80%99%20(School%20of%20Salt%20Island)%20in%20the%20island%20to%20educate%20children%20about%20trafficking%2C%20reports%20at%20least%2012%20recent%20cases%20of%20girls%20going%20missing%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20the%20danger%20of%20addictions%20that%20have%20cast%20a%20spell%20on%20the%20island.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20addiction%20to%20smoking%20or%20narcotics%20%E2%80%93%20but%20the%20promise%20of%20better%20lives%20or%20jobs%20or%20marriages.%20We%20have%20got%20some%20success%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20large%20island%20and%20we%20are%20just%20a%20small%20organisation%20with%20limited%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Soumita%20who%20had%20received%20an%20award%20from%20the%20Vice%20President%20of%20India%20for%20his%20work%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20trafficking%20and%20the%20disappearance%20of%20women%20has%20been%20a%20longstanding%20concern%2C%20but%20the%20challenges%20for%20authorities%20have%20become%20more%20complex%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic.%20They%20also%20cite%20climate%20change%20and%20the%20growth%20of%20smartphone%20usage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSchools%20were%20closed%20for%20almost%20two%20years%20forcing%20us%20to%20buy%20our%20children%20smartphones.%20How%20do%20we%20know%20whether%20they%E2%80%99re%20using%20it%20to%20study%20or%20engage%20in%20activities%20which%20can%20lead%20them%20to%20fall%20victim%20to%20such%20practices%3F%20I%20bought%20my%20daughter%20a%20phone%20to%20help%20her%20prepare%20for%20exams.%20But%20one%20day%2C%20she%20simply%20disappeared%20with%20her%20sister%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitai%20Naskar%20from%20Minakhan%20block%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20region%20of%20the%20Sundarban%20says.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20daughters%20went%20out%20to%20buy%20cosmetics%20from%20a%20village%20fair%20in%20April%20this%20year.%20They%20never%20came%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F03094617%2FScreen-Shot-2022-01-10-at-12.49.46-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2