0the%20homes%20of%20relatives%20and%20friends%20but%20did%20not%20report%20the%20incident%20to%20the%20police%20fearing%20social%20ostracisation.%20But%20one%20cannot%20say%20that%20his%20daughter%20is%20%E2%80%98missing%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20father%20of%20two%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20has%20been%20working%20outside%20for%20four%20years.%20Last%20year%2C%20she%20returned%20home%20for%20seven%20days%2C%20contributed%20money%20to%20house%20repairs%2C%20and%20took%20her%20younger%20sister%20with%20her.%20She%20looks%20different%20now%20%E2%80%93%20and%20is%20well-dressed.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20where%20she%20works%20or%20lives.%20Even%20if%20we%20ask%2C%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20specify%2C%20only%20says%20she%20is%20happy%20with%20her%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20police%20officer%20from%20the%20special%20cell%20handling%20trafficking%20in%20the%20district%20recounted%20an%20incident%20involving%20a%20teenager%20named%20Fatima.%20She%20was%20trafficked%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20made%20to%20work%20as%20a%20sex%20worker%20and%20managed%20to%20flee%20to%20Delhi%20but%20was%20then%20%E2%80%98sold%E2%80%99%20for%20Rs%2040%2C000%20to%20another%20man%20from%20Rajasthan.%20Her%20name%20was%20changed%20to%20Nandini%2C%20as%20per%20the%20wishes%20of%20her%20new%20%E2%80%98owner%E2%80%99%2C%20said%20police.%20When%20police%20rescued%20her%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20man%20who%20%E2%80%98purchased%E2%80%99%20her%20in%20Rajasthan.%20She%20cited%20financial%20stability.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%202019%20to%202021%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsatyarthi.org.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2FWest-Bengal.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20number%20of%20missing%20children%20in%20West%20Bengal%20increased%20by%2022%20%25%2C%20rising%20from%208%2C205%20to%209%2C996%2C%20whereas%20the%20national%20increase%20was%206%25%20(from%2073%2C138%20to%2077%2C535).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20around%20100%2C000%20adult%20women%20in%20Bengal%2C%20aged%2018%20and%20above%2C%20went%20missing%20in%202020%20and%202021.%20Only%2044%2C000%20have%20been%20located%20so%20far%2C%20leaving%20over%2050%2C000%20still%20unaccounted%20for.%20While%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20data%20ranks%20West%20Bengal%2010th%20in%20human%20trafficking%2C%20with%20a%20slight%20increase%20from%2027%20cases%20in%202020%20to%2029%20in%202021%2C%20the%20ground%20reality%20gives%20a%20grim%20picture.%20Many%20activists%20we%20spoke%20to%20highlight%20underreporting.%20Even%20when%20cases%20are%20reported%20to%20the%20police%2C%20a%20significant%20number%20omit%20the%20crucial%20aspect%20of%20trafficking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDearah%20Association%20for%20Social%20and%20Humanitarian%20Action%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Asha%20NGO%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20on%20the%20child%20protection%20in%20the%20bordering%20blocks%20along%20the%20Indo-Bangladesh%20border%20and%20the%20Sundarbans.%20Sanjeev%20Singh%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20organisation%2C%20narrates%20a%20case%20where%20a%20dance%20group%2C%20registered%20under%20the%20Societies%20Registration%20Act%2C%20acts%20as%20a%20front%20for%20trafficking.%20Young%20women%20are%20often%20offered%20respectable%20jobs%20at%20the%20outset%20but%20then%20go%20missing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFamilies%20find%20it%20challenging%20to%20decide%20on%20filing%20the%20complaint%20as%20their%20daughters%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20work%2C%20send%20them%20substantial%20amounts%20of%20money%20every%20month.%20The%20dynamics%20of%20trafficking%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanjeev.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20narrow%20lanes%20of%20Netaji%20Palli%20in%20Jagaddal%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20Sanjoy%20Das%20is%20still%20grappling%20with%20the%20pain%20of%20losing%20his%20daughter.%20Fourteen-year-old%20Nandita%20was%20a%20fierce%20volleyball%20player%20and%20a%20student%20at%20the%20nearby%20Aatpur%20Girls%20School.%20She%20wanted%20a%20good%20smartphone%20that%20her%20daily%20wage-earning%20father%2C%20Sanjay%2C%20could%20not%20afford.%20To%20earn%20pocket%20money%20for%20her%20goal%2C%20Nandita%20used%20to%20work%20part-time.%20One%20morning%2C%20she%20mysteriously%20disappeared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESanjoy%20reported%20the%20case%20to%20the%20police.%20During%20the%20investigation%2C%20he%20was%20informed%20that%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20found%20in%20Siwan.%20It%20was%20revealed%20that%20she%20had%20joined%20an%20orchestra%20and%20catering%20firm%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%20she%20was%20shot%20dead.%20Sanjoy%20says%20he%20has%20not%20received%20her%20death%20certificate%20or%20autopsy%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FSundarbans1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20who%20remain%20on%20the%20island%20after%20the%20men%20migrate%20take%20shelter%20in%20a%20stilt%20house%20during%20floods.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-189067%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20women%20who%20remain%20on%20the%20island%20after%20the%20men%20migrate%20take%20shelter%20in%20a%20stilt%20house%20during%20floods.%20Photo%3A%20Sayanti%20Sengupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20against%20her%20involvement%20in%20catering%20work.%20I%20heard%20that%20my%20daughter%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20during%20a%20wedding%20function%20where%20she%20went%20to%20work.%20The%20local%20police%20station%20says%20that%20the%20mention%20of%20death%20due%20to%20the%20shooting%20will%20be%20in%20the%20autopsy%20report.%20Only%20then%20will%20the%20matter%20of%20arresting%20the%20criminals%20be%20considered.%20The%20Bihar%20government%20is%20expected%20to%20send%20us%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20compensation%20and%20a%20death%20certificate.%20I%20still%20haven%E2%80%99t%20received%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanjay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20many%20speak%20of%20the%20tradition%20of%20hiring%20dancers%20for%20parties.%20Many%20of%20those%20hired%20are%20underage.%20Police%20officials%20working%20in%20this%20field%20also%20point%20out%20the%20tacit%20approval%20of%20many%20families%20who%20want%20the%20additional%20income.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20engaged%20in%20catering%20or%20dance%20groups%20for%20weddings%20are%20all%20becoming%20part%20of%20this%20cycle%20of%20crime.%20Sometimes%2C%20even%20when%20recharging%20your%20mobile%20phone%20at%20a%20shop%2C%20your%20number%20can%20be%20leaked%20to%20crime%20rackets.%20Initially%2C%20there%20are%20missed%20calls%2C%20then%20regular%20contact%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20they%20are%20lured%20with%20lucrative%20offers%20to%20disappear%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%20police%20official%20from%20North%2024%20Parganas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20senior%20police%20officer%20Sukhendu%20Hira%20also%20speaks%20of%20such%20methods.%20Hira%20says%20there%20are%20some%20age-old%20ways%20young%20women%20are%20trafficked%3A%20they%20are%20given%20work%20or%20married%20off%20or%20lured%20with%20promises%20of%20love.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocal%20acquaintances%20in%20the%20area%20are%20also%20noted%20to%20facilitate%20trafficking.%20These%20criminal%20activities%20often%20go%20unreported%20due%20to%20families%E2%80%99%20struggles%20with%20poverty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20victims%20often%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20recruitment%20racket%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20police%20officer%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*Names%20changed%20on%20request.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701135023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F05191621%2FIMG_6847.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-the-nature-of-human-trafficking-has-changed-in-bengal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20numbers%20have%20increased%2C%20nowadays%20many%20families%20are%20reluctant%20to%20lodge%20police%20complaints.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-the-nature-of-human-trafficking-has-changed-in-bengal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rita%20Hollingsworth%2C%20Longtime%20Entertainment%20Publicist%2C%20Dies%20at%2061%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701134521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FRitaHollingsworth-1.jpg%3Fcrop%3D189px%252C595px%252C2642px%252C1484px%26resize%3D1000%252C563%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235810539%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rita%20Hollingsworth%2C%20a%20longtime%20publicist%20for%20entertainment%20clients%20and%20non-profit%20organizations%2C%20died%20Nov.%2016%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20She%20was%2061.%20Her%20husband%20Jeff%20Hollingsworth%20said%20she%20had%20suffered%20a%20intracerebral%20brain%20hemorrhage.%20When%20working%20at%20the%20Lee%20Solters%20Company%2C%20she%20represented%20clients%20including%20Barbra%20Streisand%2C%20Michael%20Jackson%2C%20Liza%20Minnelli%20and%20Neil%20Diamond%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pat%20Saperstein%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Frita-hollingsworth-dead-entertainment-publicist-1235810539%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2F