20you%20become%20a%20public%20servant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20UPSC%20allows%20you%20to%20broaden%20your%20knowledge%20horizon.%20If%20I%20had%20been%20just%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20have%20not%20read%20geography%2C%20civics%2C%20or%20economics.%20During%20preparation%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20about%20my%20country%20in%20detail.%20This%20is%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2035-year-old%2C%20who%20did%20not%20take%20medicine%20as%20her%20optional%20but%20a%20new%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSaloni-Sidana-2-1700746879-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334805%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaloni%20completed%20her%20MBBS%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Lady%20Hardinge%20Medical%20College%20in%202012.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaloni%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20knowledge%20helped%20her%20crack%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https